\plain {\b\f8\fs24 Contents } \par \f8\fs20
\par
The Nonogram Solver v1.2 for Windows is capable of solving all of the standard \ul\f8\fs20 Nonogram\plain \ul\v\f8\fs20 typnono\plain \f8\fs20  style of puzzles. To learn more about Nonograms, see \uldb\f8\fs20 Introducing Nonograms\plain \uldb\v\f8\fs20 introduction\plain \f8\fs20 . To learn more about the changes from v1.0 for DOS, see \uldb\f8\fs20 Changes for Windows\plain \uldb\v\f8\fs20 changes\plain \f8\fs20 . To learn more about the changes from earlier Windows versions, see \uldb\f8\fs20 Changes from earlier versions\plain \uldb\v\f8\fs20 winchng\plain \f8\fs20 . \par
\par
\par
